/goosefeatherscafe.com/s/menus", description: "Proudly serving the Savannah area since 1986, this bustling but cozy café fuses the dining ambiance found in Lower Manhattan's classic corner cafes with Southern Charm and Hospitality. Love breakfast? Goose Feathers Café serves go-to breakfast favorites like our warm bagels, handmade sweet preserve-filled and stuffed butter croissants, warm waffles with fresh fruit, and Eggs Benedict Savannah style served on our made from scratch butter croissant buns. For lunch, enjoy the soup of the day and sandwiches, Grilled Panini and a variety of green salads. Other popular menu items include the Bacon Mushroom Chicken Sandwich, Italian Panini or vegetarian-friendly Veggie Panini and Black Bean Burrito. Be sure to save room for a serious selection of sweets made from scratch including homemade cookies, cakes, bread pudding, Pecan Pie and our famous whoopie pies. Bon appetit!", photoCount: "642.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 33, \"count2\": 68, \"count3\": 278, \"count4\": 934, \"count5\": 2263}", email: "cafe@goosefeatherscafe.com", website: "http://www.goosefeatherscafe.com", rankingPosition: "20.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 480, \"openHours\": \"08:00\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}], [{\"open\": 450, \"openHours\": \"07:30\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}], [], [{\"open\": 450, \"openHours\": \"07:30\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}], [{\"open\": 450, \"openHours\": \"07:30\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}], [{\"open\": 450, \"openHours\": \"07:30\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}], [{\"open\": 480, \"openHours\": \"08:00\", \"close\": 870, \"closeHours\": \"14:30\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/New_York\"}", address: "39 Barnard St Between Broughton & Congress, Downtown, Savannah, GA 31401-2519", neighborhoodLocations: "[{\"id\": \"20932022\", \"name\": \"Downtown\"}]", dishes: ["Pasta", "Bagels", "Baguette", "Burrito", "Cheesecake", "Corned Beef",